Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:38.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an5\blur5\fad(300,300)\fscx100\fscy100\pos(960,1035)}狂わないなんて信じていないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:45.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an5\blur5\fad(300,300)\fscx100\fscy100\pos(960,1035)}進もうと急かすような秒針
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:46.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an5\blur5\fad(300,300)\fscx80\fscy80\pos(960,990)}Close-set mind
